pr_description:
@casesandberg 

For #365

I only added `onSwatchHover` for `CompactPicker`, but if you'd like me to add it to any picker that wraps Swatch, I'd be happy to. And in general, I'm open to any ideas for getting this functionality in.

@casesandberg 

For #365

I only added `onSwatchHover` for `CompactPicker`, but if you'd like me to add it to any picker that wraps Swatch, I'd be happy to. And in general, I'm open to any ideas for getting this functionality in.

@casesandberg 

For #365

I only added `onSwatchHover` for `CompactPicker`, but if you'd like me to add it to any picker that wraps Swatch, I'd be happy to. And in general, I'm open to any ideas for getting this functionality in.

@casesandberg 

For #365

I only added `onSwatchHover` for `CompactPicker`, but if you'd like me to add it to any picker that wraps Swatch, I'd be happy to. And in general, I'm open to any ideas for getting this functionality in.

